      <p>My career has taken me across a range of settings domestically and internationally—from after-school and wilderness therapy programs to outpatient and HIV clinics. These experiences shaped my expertise in working with sexual health and relationships, intimate partner violence, trauma, emergency responders, and healthcare workers.</p>
      <p>I moved to Colorado in 2016 to have more opportunities to rock climb, hike, and ski—things that were a bit harder to come by in my home state of Michigan (which I still hold dear to my heart). </p>
